OL,3,CMan admits murdering 76-year-old two
OL,4,Cyears after grievous bodily harm arrest
OL,6,FA man has admitted murdering a 76-year-
OL,7,Fold in Gloucestershire nearly two
OL,8,Fyears ago.
OL,10,FAnthony Gardiner, 66 and of Daniels
OL,11,FRoad in Stroud, attacked John Coxon at
OL,12,Fhis home in Stonehouse in January 2022.
OL,14,FPolice were called to the scene on
OL,15,FPark Road to reports that Mr Coxon had
OL,16,Fsustained a head injury.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital, where he
OL,19,Fremained for several months until he
OL,20,Fdied on 25 March.
