OL,6,FGardiner was initially arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing grievous bodily
OL,8,Fharm. Following the death of Mr Coxon,
OL,9,Fa murder investigation was launched
OL,10,Fand Gardiner was re-arrested.
OL,12,FDuring a hearing at Bristol Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Thursday 12 December,
OL,14,FGardiner pleaded guilty to murder.
OL,16,FFollowing the hearing, Detective
OL,17,FInspector Adam Stacey said: "Gardiner
OL,18,Fwas arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm after he had
OL,20,Fassaulted Mr Coxon at his home address.
